<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 columns centered">
    <h1 class="title"><strong>Produce done right.</strong></h1>
    <p class="subhead">Selected for nutrition, flavor, and freshness. Then delivered.</p>
    <hr />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 columns centered">
    <ul class="small-block-grid-3 medium-block-grid-5 featurettes">
      <li>
        <a href="#ft-fresh">
          <i class="fa fa-3x fa-pagelines"></i>
          <p><strong>Fresh and nutritious</strong><br /> Freshly harvested just hours before delivery</p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li><a href="#ft-diverse">
        <i class="fa fa-3x fa-star-o"></i>
        <p><strong>Diverse</strong><br />Wide selection of ripe local offerings</p></a>
      </li>
      <li><a href="#ft-convenient">
        <i class="fa fa-3x fa-truck"></i>
        <p><strong>Convenient</strong><br />One subscription for all your fresh produce needs</p></a>
      </li>
      <li><a href="#ft-cook">
        <i class="fa fa-3x fa-cutlery"></i>
        <p><strong>Easy to prepare</strong><br />Simple preparation tips included</p></a>
      </li>
      <li><a href="#ft-honest">
        <i class="fa fa-3x fa-thumbs-up"></i>
        <p><strong>Honestly sourced</strong><br />From local farms with good practices</p></a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row feature" id="ft-fresh">
  <div class="small-12 columns panel-box">
    <div class="centered">
      <i class="fa fa-3x fa-pagelines"></i>
      <h2>Fresh and nutritious</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-12 medium-6 medium-offset-1 columns featurette-text">
        <p>We’re obsessed with maximizing the freshness of the vegetables we deliver. Often, the items in your box are delivered within <strong>24 hours</strong> of being harvested by local farmers.</p><p>Less time in storage means vegetables keep more of their essential nutrients, stay fresh longer in your refrigerator, and taste how they are supposed to taste.
        </p>

      </div>
      <div class="small-12 medium-5 columns caption"><%= image_tag('greenbeans.jpg') %><small>Freshness is important for nutrition. Green beans can lose up to 77% of their vitamin C content from just one week's worth of cold storage.</small></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row feature" id="ft-diverse">
  <div class="small-12 columns panel-box">
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-12 medium-5 columns"><%= image_tag('sungold-tomato.jpg'); %><p class="small">Sun gold tomatoes have nearly the highest sugar and lowest acid levels of any tomatoes, but have thin skins that make them unsuitable for long transport. Find them in our summer boxes.</p></div>
      
      <div class="small-12 medium-7 columns featurette-text">
        <div class="centered"><i class="fa fa-3x fa-star-o"></i>
        <h2>Diverse, ripe, and local</h2></div>
        <div class="featurette-text"><p>Most supermarket produce today is selected for high yield and long shelf-life. The local farmers we source from however, can grow more diverse and delicate varieties because they don’t need to worry about packing and shipping long distances.</p><p> Experience a whole new world of produce, with everything from pink baby ginger to juicy gooseberries. 
        </p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br /><br /><br />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row feature" id="ft-convenient">
  <div class="small-12 columns panel-box">
    <div class="centered"><a><i class="fa fa-3x fa-truck"></i></a>
    <h2>Simple and convenient</h2></div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-6 small-offset-1 columns featurette-text">
        <p>
          Choose a box that fits your lifestyle and subscribe. Select whether you'd like vegetables for raw consumption or for cooking, and choose the amount of fruit you'd like to get. 
        </p>
        <p>Then sit back. We fill your box each week with fresh ingredients from local farms and deliver it to your door. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="small-5 columns">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="small-12 columns centered">
            <br />
            <p>Starting from $20 per week. <br />Cancel anytime.</p>
            <%= link_to 'Get started!', new_box_path, html_options = {class: "get-started-button", id: "features-ourboxes"} %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row feature" id="ft-cook">
  <div class="small-12 columns panel-box">
    <div class="centered"><i class="fa fa-3x fa-cutlery"></i>
    <h2>Easy to prepare</h2></div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-8 small-offset-2 columns featurette-text"><p>When you’re working with quality ingredients, creating flavorful meals becomes a lot easier. With each box, we include simple preparation tips and recipes designed to bring out the best in our produce whether you choose to cook it or eat it raw.
      </p></div>
    </div>
    <br /><br />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row feature" id="ft-honest">
  <div class="small-12 columns panel-box">
    <div class="centered"><i class="fa fa-3x fa-thumbs-up"></i>
    <h2>Honestly sourced</h2></div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-6 small-offset-1 columns featurette-text">
        <p>We make an effort to tour the farms we source from and see their growing practices firsthand so we can share that information with you. Beyond the quality of the produce itself, we also look for farms that:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>are family-owned and operated</li>
          <li>refrain from using genetically modified seed varieties</li>
          <li>care about maintaining and improving the health of the soil and the environment</li>
          <li>use no or low spray growing practices</li>
          <li>minimize external inputs (like synthetic fertilizers) and waste outputs</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Every delivery comes with information about where each vegetable comes from and the growing practices on the farms.  
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="small-5 columns">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="small-12 columns centered">
            <br /><br /><br />
            <p>Learn more about our sourcing practices</p>
            <%= link_to 'Our farms', welcome_farms_path, html_options = {class: "get-started-button"} %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
